### Array Buffer and Data Views:

Working with raw binary data using `ArrayBuffer` and `DataView`:

```javascript
let buffer = new ArrayBuffer(16);
let view = new DataView(buffer);

view.setInt32(0, 42); // Set a 32-bit integer at byte offset 0
view.setFloat64(4, Math.PI); // Set a 64-bit floating-point number at byte offset 4

